The npm packages @rhwp/core and @rhwp/editor are used as dependencies. The
WebAssembly binary (public/rhwp_bg.wasm) is fetched from @rhwp/core at install
time (see copy-wasm.mjs, run via the "postinstall" script) and is not committed.

This repository bundles a build of rhwp-studio (the rhwp web editor) under
public/studio/, redistributed under the MIT License, so that the embedded
editor includes the latest features (e.g. table resizing). rhwp-studio is part
of the rhwp project (https://github.com/edwardkim/rhwp), Copyright (c) 2025-2026
Edward Kim, MIT License.
